bengal   (   /baŋla/ or   bônggo /bɔŋɡo/ ) is a geographical and ethno - linguistic region in the eastern part of the indian subcontinent , at the apex of the bay of bengal and dominated by the fertile ganges delta .

rebel yell : hey , hey we 're the naxalites , a maoist rebel group with origins in the bengal region of this country

